      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "output.ask write-target annotates as (ask) downstream \u2014 its reflected\nreturn type is Data\u003CAsk\u003E. Ask.ToString() returns the Answer string so\ndownstream code can still interpolate %answer% as text, but the type\nidentity in the snapshot stays \u0022ask\u0022. (Test-designer\u0027s original spec\nsaid \u0022string\u0022; reconfirmed with Ingi 2026-05-27 \u2014 match reflected type\nfor consistency with every other action.)",
